13
0:00:50.16,000 --> 0:00:53,000
so it's the same now, 30 years later,

14
0:00:53.16,000 --> 0:00:57,000
even though our economy has gone up 80 percent, per capita.

15
0:00:57.16,000 --> 0:01:,000
