this is the bustling squatter city

50
0:02:31.16,000 --> 0:02:35,000
of Kibera, near Nairobi --

51
0:02:35.16,000 --> 0:02:37,000
they see action. They see opportunity.

52
0:02:37.16,000 --> 0:02:4,000
