91
0:04:26.16,000 --> 0:04:3,000
The main event is, these are not people crushed by poverty.

92
0:04:30.16,000 --> 0:04:32,000
These are people busy getting out of poverty

93
0:04:32.16,000 --> 0:04:34,000
just as fast as they can.

94
0:04:34.16,000 --> 0:04:36,000
