112
0:05:21.16,000 --> 0:05:24,000
And one of the main events are these ad-hoc schools.

113
0:05:24.16,000 --> 0:05:28,000
Parents pool their money to hire some local teachers

114
0:05:28.16,000 --> 0:05:3,000
